ed cucumber, scrape down the middle of cucumber to scoop out and cut in small pieces, Cut tomatoes and olives in halves, carrots and radish in slice, drain well corn and petit pois and chopped onion.<br><br>In a salad bowl mix all ingredients less walnut and toss well to combine flavors.&nbsp;To serve sprinkle walnuts.&nbsp;You can use hot or cold rice, but with room temperature rice is delicious.<br>\n',6,0,0,2,0,35,13,7,8,10,6,15,'../files/recipes/Mediterran Salad.JPG','2014-05-21 23:30:36',NULL,0,0,0,0,0,0,NULL);
